{
  "info": {
    "name": "The Daily Plugin",
    "description": "Postman collection for Slopsmith 'The Daily' plugin API. Contains all endpoints for daily setlists, gameplay, leaderboards, shop, inventory, and system checks.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Create/select an environment with variables:\n   - `baseUrl` - Plugin base URL (e.g., http://localhost:8080)\n   - `installId` - Your install ID (can be any unique string)\n   - `displayName` - Your leaderboard display name\n\n## Quick Start\n- Start with **GET /today** to fetch today's setlist\n- Use **POST /mark** to mark songs/nodes complete\n- Check **GET /leaderboard** for rankings",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "installId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "displayName",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Daily Setlist",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Today",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/plugins/the_daily/today",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "plugins", "the_daily", "today"]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Daily-Install-Id",
                "value": "{{installId}}"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Fetch today's daily setlist. Returns the day's songs, modifier info, map (if in Map Mode), progress state, and inventory.\n\n**Response includes:**\n- `date`, `day_name`, `day_number`\n- `modifier` (id, label, description, icon)\n- `songs[]` with cf_id, artist, title, has_locally, done\n- `map` object (nodes, edges, boss, lanes) if Map Mode active\n- `progress` (done/total)\n- `is_complete` boolean\n- `inventory` with items and tokens"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.environment.get('installId')) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('installId', 'test-' + Date.now());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Setlist by Date",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/plugins/the_daily/setlist/{{date}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "plugins", "the_daily", "setlist", "{{date}}"]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Fetch a historical setlist by date.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `date` - ISO date string (e.g., 2026-04-22)\n\n**Constraints:**\n- Cannot request future dates\n- Returns 400 for invalid date format",
            "variable": [
              {
                "key": "date",
                "value": "2026-04-22",
                "type": "string"
              }
            ]
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.environment.get('installId')) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('installId', 'test-' + Date.now());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Gameplay",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Mark Song/Node Complete",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/plugins/the_daily/mark",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "plugins", "the_daily", "mark"]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"cf_id\": 12345,\n  \"node_id\": \"boss\",\n  \"install_id\": \"{{installId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Mark a song or node as played/completed.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `cf_id` (required) - CustomsForge song ID\n- `node_id` (optional) - Node ID for map mode\n- `action` (optional) - \"commit\" to commit to a node path\n- `install_id` - Your install ID\n- `duration_played` (optional) - Seconds played (min 30 to count)\n\n**Actions:**\n- Omit `action` for standard play tracking\n- Use `\"action\": \"commit\"` to lock in a path choice at a choice node"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.environment.get('installId')) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('installId', 'test-' + Date.now());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Use Item",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/plugins/the_daily/use-item",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "plugins", "the_daily", "use-item"]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"item_id\": \"boss_reroll\",\n  \"node_id\": \"boss\",\n  \"install_id\": \"{{installId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Use a consumable item (boss re-roll, lane re-roll).\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `item_id` (required) - \"boss_reroll\" or \"lane_reroll\"\n- `node_id` (required for lane_reroll) - Node to re-roll\n- `install_id` - Your install ID\n\n**Item Effects:**\n- `boss_reroll` - Replaces the boss song with a new one from the modifier pool\n- `lane_reroll` - Re-rolls non-boss songs on a single lane"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.environment.get('installId')) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('installId', 'test-' + Date.now());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
