            },
            "description": "Clear a specific node in Map Mode.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `nodeId` - The node ID to clear\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `install_id` - Your install ID\n- `cf_id` - Song ID to mark complete at this node"
          },
